                    <br/>Bestil på: <a class="h4 tlf" href="tel:004598935566">98 93 55 66</a>
                </p>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="opening-hours">
        <div class="opening-days-list">
            <ul class="footer-list">
                <li class=" list-header">Åbningstider</li>
                <li>Mandag - fredag:</li>
                <li>Lørdag:</li>
                <li>Søndag:</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="opening-hours-list">
            <ul class="footer-list">
                <li id="opening-hours-title-display-none" class=" list-header">---</li>
                <li>11:00-22:00</li>
                <li>11:00-22:00</li>
                <li>12:00-22:00</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
       
    </div>
    
    <div>
        <ul class="footer-list">
            <li class="footer-item list-header">Om hjemmesiden</li>
            <li class="footer-item">
